questions.quote: Hey Bob. What's with you? You gotta problem?  You see that look he gave me?
Oh, was he? Was he? I guess the cable man doesn't like to be kept waiting.
The wall had just come down, and you told me you wanted to be part of the celebration.
Tennis courts? W-w-what about the yard? Where do they have the gang fights?
Hey you know this is the first time we've ever seen each other naked.
And you know what else? He picked up that woman in the coffee shop.
If I'm gettin' him a new fur, I'm not chippin' in on a gift, too.
What the hell is this? "George, Elaine and I went to see Chunnel ... with Jerry." With Jerry, huh? With Jerry! Great. Great!  Probably went to the 84th St. That's where I always go with Jerry.
So, she's the loser of the group. Every group has someone that they all make fun of.. Like us with Elaine.
Well, I see what's going on in here. I am smack dab in the middle of a good old fashioned cat fight.
